      null,
      "Web Views enforce ",
      [
        "stencil-route-link",
        {
          "url": "/docs/reference/glossary#cors"
        },
        "CORS"
      ],
      ", so it's important that external services properly handle cross-origin requests. See the ",
      [
        "stencil-route-link",
        {
          "url": "/docs/troubleshooting/cors"
        },
        "CORS FAQs"
      ],
      " for information on dealing with CORS in Ionic apps."
